<% @email_title = "eLMo password changed" %>

<h2>Password Successfully Updated</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @resource.full_name || @resource.email.split('@').first %>!</p>

<p>This is to confirm that the password for your eLMo account has been successfully changed.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Security details:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li>Change made on: <%= Time.current.in_time_zone("Asia/Manila").strftime("%B %d, %Y at %l:%M %p PHT") %></li>
    <li>IP address: <%= @resource.current_sign_in_ip || "Unknown" %></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>Your account remains secure and you can continue using eLMo with your new password.</p>

<div class="alert-box">
  <p><strong>Didn't make this change?</strong> If you didn't change your password, please contact our support team immediately. Someone may have unauthorized access to your account.</p>
</div>

<p><strong>Security reminders:</strong></p>
<ul style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.6;">
  <li>Keep your password secure and don't share it with anyone</li>
  <li>Use a unique password for your eLMo account</li>
  <li>Consider enabling two-factor authentication for extra security</li>
  <li>Sign out of eLMo when using shared or public computers</li>
</ul>

<p>Thank you for keeping your eLMo account secure!</p>
